The paper deals with graph parameters and algorithms for counting subgraph copies, which are topics that are commonly studied in discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational complexity (cs.CC), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also uses techniques from graph theory (cs.CG) and combinatorics (cs.GT).
